{"ID":"20260609124709-gzzi1ph","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260609124709-gzzi1ph","title":"2023年全国乙卷","type":"doc","updated":"20260609124837"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260609124730-l79j81m","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124730-l79j81m","updated":"20260609124730"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"郭老头、耿老头，俩老头，这两个老头，从前面看，像五十岁；从后面看，像三十岁，他们今年都已经做过七十整寿了，身体真好！郭老头能吃饭，斤半烙饼卷成一卷，攥在手里，蘸一点汁，几口就下去了。他这辈子没有牙疼过。耿老头能喝酒。他拿了茶碗上供销社去打酒，一手接酒，一手交钱，售货员找了钱给他，他亮着个空碗：“酒呢？”售货员有点忧伤：记得是打给他了呀！——售货员低头数钱的功夫，二两酒已经进了他的肚了，俩老头非常“要好”——这地方的方言，“要好”是爱干净爱整齐的意思，不论什么时候，上唇的胡子平崭乌黑，下巴的胡子刮得溜光。浑身的衣服，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":"袖子是袖子，领子是领子"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，一个纽扣也不短。俩老头还都爱穿靸鞋，斜十字实纳帮，皮梁、荡底，是托人在北京步云斋买的。这种鞋过去是专门卖给抬轿的轿夫穿的，后来拉包月车的车夫也爱穿，抱脚，精神！"}]},{"ID":"20260609124730-lb27jsj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124730-lb27jsj","updated":"20260609124730"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"俩老头焦不离孟，孟不离焦。"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":"年下办年货，一起去；四月十八奶奶庙庙会，一起去；开会，一起到场；送人情出份子，一起进门"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。生产队有事找他们，队长总是说：“去！找找俩老头！”“俩老头”不是“两个老头”的意思，是说他们特别亲密的关系。类似“哥俩”、“姐俩”，按说应该叫他们“老头俩”，不过没有这么说话的，所以人们只能叫他们“俩老头”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609124709-fz9vkra","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609124709-fz9vkra","updated":"20260609124742"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"题目"}]},{"ID":"20260609124742-phdkrcm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124742-phdkrcm","updated":"20260609124742"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"17．下列句子中的“能”与文中加点的“能”，意义和用法相同的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260609124742-yajm68z","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124742-yajm68z","updated":"20260609124742"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．她尽量高高地跳起脚尖，希望车厢里的人能看见她的脸。"}]},{"ID":"20260609124742-bsmdds2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124742-bsmdds2","updated":"20260609124742"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．我们班同学就数他能说，讲起话来口若悬河滔滔不绝。"}]},{"ID":"20260609124742-xjoo0p4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124742-xjoo0p4","updated":"20260609124742"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．新颁布的控烟条例规定，绝大多数公共场所都不能吸烟。"}]},{"ID":"20260609124742-kc6h949","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124742-kc6h949","updated":"20260609124742"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．以前这条小河上没有桥，人们只能涉水而过，非常不便。"}]},{"ID":"20260609124742-87vti8p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124742-87vti8p","updated":"20260609124742"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"18．下列句子中画横线部分与文中画横线部分的语句，用法和作用相同的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260609124742-3hc0s07","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124742-3hc0s07","updated":"20260609124742"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．稗子的叶很像稻叶。但"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":"稻子是稻子，稗子是稗子"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，要分清楚。"}]},{"ID":"20260609124742-qo709sc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124742-qo709sc","updated":"20260609124742"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．说话办事一定要公私分明，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":"公是公，私是私"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，不能公器私用。"}]},{"ID":"20260609124742-qqdtzay","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124742-qqdtzay","updated":"20260609124742"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．从今以后，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":"你的是你的，我的是我的"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，咱们俩井水不犯河。"}]},{"ID":"20260609124742-jimy8st","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124742-jimy8st","updated":"20260609124742"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．瞧那个小姑娘，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":"眼睛是眼睛，鼻子是鼻子"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，真是个美人胚子。"}]},{"ID":"20260609124742-q3hohid","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124742-q3hohid","updated":"20260609124742"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"19．文中画波浪线的句子如改成：“年下办年货、四月十八奶奶庙庙会、开会、送人情出份子，都一起去。”语义基本相同，但原文表达效果更好，为什么？"}]},{"ID":"20260609124709-k5i9kik","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609124709-k5i9kik","updated":"20260609124804"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"答案"}]},{"ID":"20260609124804-4mhmia3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124804-4mhmia3","updated":"20260609124804"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"17．B    18．D    19．①原句使用排比和反复修辞，原句四句结构相似，句式整齐，节奏感强，并且“一起”共出现四次，更能突出俩人关系密切，形影不离；改句没有排比、反复修辞，不能起到突出强调的作用。"}]},{"ID":"20260609124804-1k2a4h8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124804-1k2a4h8","updated":"20260609124804"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"②原句为短句，改句是长单句，原句使用短句更符合整个文段口语化的特点。"}]},{"ID":"20260609124804-qpnp1rf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124804-qpnp1rf","updated":"20260609124804"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"③原句使用“到场”“进门”这样的动词，让描写更细腻，更有画面感；改句只用“去”则没有这种效果。"}]},{"ID":"20260609124709-uhtrdtj","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609124709-uhtrdtj","updated":"20260609124837"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"解析"}]},{"ID":"20260609124837-lbntszr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124837-lbntszr","updated":"20260609124837"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"17．本题考查学生理解词语含义的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260609124837-0ymdk3j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124837-0ymdk3j","updated":"20260609124837"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"文中的“能”含义是“擅长”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609124837-tbrtu8l","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124837-tbrtu8l","updated":"20260609124837"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A.“能”，动词，“能够，可以”；"}]},{"ID":"20260609124837-odcnt9r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124837-odcnt9r","updated":"20260609124837"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B.“能”，动词，“擅长，善于”；"}]},{"ID":"20260609124837-w0ogvcu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124837-w0ogvcu","updated":"20260609124837"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C.“能”，动词，“能够，可以”；"}]},{"ID":"20260609124837-732xvcn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124837-732xvcn","updated":"20260609124837"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D.“能”，动词，“能够，可以”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609124837-jteviuk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124837-jteviuk","updated":"20260609124837"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选B。"}]},{"ID":"20260609124837-wiiwl36","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124837-wiiwl36","updated":"20260609124837"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"18．本题考查学生分析句子的用法和作用的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260609124837-2fqft4w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124837-2fqft4w","updated":"20260609124837"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"文中画横线部分的语句属于描写性语句，突出强调描写对象“俩老头”穿的衣服干净整齐的特点；"}]},{"ID":"20260609124837-qtxivm7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124837-qtxivm7","updated":"20260609124837"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A.“稻子是稻子，稗子是稗子”属于说明性语言，突出强调“稻子和稗子”是有本质区别的，应该分清楚；"}]},{"ID":"20260609124837-t5f6op6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124837-t5f6op6","updated":"20260609124837"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B.“公是公，私是私”属于议论性语言，突出强调应公私分明的观点；"}]},{"ID":"20260609124837-4c40clh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124837-4c40clh","updated":"20260609124837"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C.“你的是你的，我的是我的”属于人物语言描写，突出强调与对方划清界限；"}]},{"ID":"20260609124837-tm1q4p9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124837-tm1q4p9","updated":"20260609124837"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D.“眼睛是眼睛，鼻子是鼻子”属于描写性语句，突出强调描写对象“小姑娘”长得漂亮的特点。"}]},{"ID":"20260609124837-j2fzdvo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124837-j2fzdvo","updated":"20260609124837"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选D。"}]},{"ID":"20260609124837-f1qrtz6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124837-f1qrtz6","updated":"20260609124837"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"19．本题考查学生赏析句子的表达效果的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260609124837-88cnp0l","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124837-88cnp0l","updated":"20260609124837"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"从修辞角度分析，原句“年下办年货，一起去；四月十八奶奶庙庙会，一起去；开会，一起到场；送人情出份子，一起进门”使用了排比修辞；“一起”反复出现四次，运用反复修辞。改句没有运用修辞，原句的排比和反复修辞使描写的性语句起到了突出强调的作用，突出强调了俩老头关系密切，形影不离。"}]},{"ID":"20260609124837-cj0pw2t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124837-cj0pw2t","updated":"20260609124837"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"从句式和语体色彩分析，结合“郭老头、耿老头，俩老头”“攥在手里”“几口就下去了”等语言特点来看，整个文段运用的是口语化的语言。划线句原文为短句，改句为长单句，短句属于口语的一种特点，这与整个文段短句化的口语特点相符，而改句为一般的长单句，与整个文段的语体不协调。"}]},{"ID":"20260609124837-oymx4dj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609124837-oymx4dj","updated":"20260609124837"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"从用词角度分析，原句比改句多使用了“到场”“进门”这样的动词，动词的加入，让描写性语言更生动，生动地描写了俩老头一起来开会，一起去送人情出份子的事件，让语言更有画面感。改句没有使用这样生动的动词，因此没有这样的效果。"}]}]}